	   <tr><td colspan=2>You will always suck at soloing because it is simple you are meant to fight a mob from the backside meaning from the front you won't do high damage and you can't take many hits.&nbsp;&nbsp;Find a tank who can taunt and learn to always stay on backside of enemy and you will do fine. Rogue are not meant to solo, you want to beable to stand toe to toe with a enemy then be a warrior, if you want to sneak around, steal, and stab things when they are not looking then be a rogue!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
